full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/18/2023 UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTIC Form G-139 (Rev. 5/23/55) Immigration & Naturalization Service 70 Columbus Avenue Requesting Office Number File No. New York 23, N.Y. 0300 (Address of requesting office) A10 090 167 G-JS AR No. (If different than File No.) AGENCY ADDRESS CHECK REQUEST Date TO: April 16, 1956 SOCIAL SECURITY ADMINISTRATION THROUGH OFFICER IN CHARGE CHIEF, RECORDS ADMINISTRATION BRANCH ALTIMORE, MD. CENTRAL OFFICE S-2073674 Please check all alien indices. The whereabouts of the alien named herein are being sought by this Service. It is requested that, in accordance with the provisions of section 290 of the Immigration and Nationality Act, all available information be furnished from your records which may be of assistance in establishing his location and identity. Indicate discrepancies, if any, and insert missing or more recent information, if available, on the face or reverse of this form.
